op of my head, I believe I lose around 5% haste and 40hp, and gain 9 raw ac, 5 fire, 20 cold and 10 magic resist.  Figured it was time I stopped lurking and actually posted something =)<br><br>Grakk Gai'shae<br>59 Troll Warrior<br>Amber Order, E'ci<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/utalicmoore.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Talic Moore</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://forums.interealms.com/ranger/images/icons/Yin_Yang.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Hero of the Realms</span><br>  Posts: 703<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/5/02 7:04:24 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1759.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.eyesonff.com/ff1/fighter.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Older Topic: Lodi&amp;rbb vs. cof</span><hr size=1> Perhaps it's just me, but the idea of selling dragon loot bugs me. Despite this I'd stick with the Cloak of Flames. 5% haste is, honestly, a bit more important than 9 raw ac and the other stats if you ask me.<br><br>Merely my opinion though. Perhaps I'm dumb. <p><img src=http://www.warghoul.com/images/talicsig.jpg ></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/udraxusmt.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Draxus MT</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 70<br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/5/02 11:28:24 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1759.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Older Topic: Lodi&amp;rbb vs. cof</span><hr size=1> After figuring for Agi AC, it's even less favorable. <p><br><table><td>